headline: Realtor.com速 Reveals the Top Housing Markets for 2026
summary: Realtor.com速's annual ranking of the Top Housing Markets for 2026 shows a notable geographic shift from a year ago: while last year's top metros were concentrated in the South and West, the markets projected to see the strongest combined growth in home sales and prices in 2026 are now overwhelmingly in the Northeast and Midwest. Hartford, Conn., Rochester, N.Y., and Worcester, Mass., lead the 2026 list.
